title: Todd Gurley to Atlanta, Melvin Gordon to Denver, and a Fantasy Mailbag! | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
We break down the recent happenings in free agency, including Todd Gurley to the Falcons, Melvin Gordon to the Broncos, Emmanuel Sanders to the Saints, and more (1:10). Then we open the first fantasy mailbag of the 2020 season (31:45).
Hosts: Danny Heifetz, Danny Kelly, and Craig Horlbeck
